# HARNESS_LOCK artifact — frozen snapshot of the dev harness at the moment Gate 5 closed.
# Usage: lives at docs/sdlc/harness/harness.lock. Regenerated only on intentional re-install.
# Treat this like a package lockfile: commit it; review changes carefully.

